snippet.title: SNES Super Ghouls 'n Ghosts Video Walkthrough
snippet.description:
This is a video walkthrough / playthrough / runthrough / etc of the Super Nintendo game Super Ghouls 'n Ghosts.

It's not exactly a no hit run, but close to it.  I do get transformed during the first runthrough the levels, and I lose my shield in the second.  Thankfully though I get through it more or less unscathed otherwise.  I was hoping that this would have been the one I go through perfectly, but it appears it just wasn't meant to be...Oh well...

With this video, I think I'm finally done uploading GnG games....Quite the relief actually... :P
